keyFacts: The document is an email chain from November 2021 concerning a proffer agreement, indicating ongoing legal or investigative proceedings related to child exploitation and human trafficking.
It involves the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force and an Assistant United States Attorney from the Southern District of New York.
References to an attached '302' suggest an FBI interview report (Form FD-302) is part of the documentation.
The correspondence shows a collaborative effort between law enforcement and prosecution in finalizing legal agreements.
The email chain highlights procedural steps in obtaining and initialing proffer agreements as part of an investigation.
